[DEFNAME BC_MESSAGES]
BC_MESSAGE_1 Avril Lavigne is HOT.
BC_MESSAGE_2 So is Elisha Cuthbert.
BC_MESSAGE_3 Ahum, this was scripted by Exercisto.
BC_MESSAGE_4 Surprised? Why?
BC_MESSAGE_5 Right.
BC_MESSAGE_6 Did I mention Avril is a hottie?
BC_MESSAGE_7 Why the hell did I make 10 messages in the first place?
BC_MESSAGE_8 I'm getting typing blisters, I am.
